(secondQuint)Responses of Premature Infants to Measles-Mumps-Rubella (MMR) and Varicella Vaccines.

 The purpose of this study is to see if the MMR and chickenpox vaccines work as well in premature infants as in children that were carried to full term.

 A group of children who were carried full-term will be matched for age, sex, and race and will be used for comparison.

